Room.Name: Overland Drive
Room.ShortDescription: You are walking along Overland Drive, east of the Circle-Bar Ranch House.
Room.LongDescription: The Circle-Bar Ranch House provides much of the meat and meat by-products that are consumed by the citizens of Oceancrest. Many of the best butchers have at one time worked for the Circle-Bar Ranch, preparing the cattle for consumption. The Cattle Ranch is located west of the Ranch House. The Chateau Richland Grape Orchard is located to the east.
